cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

The paper deals with the compression and acceleration of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves encoding and quantization, which are also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the use of FPGA and ASIC for efficient implementation suggests a possible connection to computer architecture (cs.AR).
